{"tid":2241070,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：已對武肺免疫 我要親吻所有支持者","createTime":"2020-10-13T05:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T22:48:16.000Z","uid":66271,"like":59,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"853a4029b1481c9e51e266074757b4743bacdb32","tid":2241070,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2775000/2775488/131020_rally_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2775000%2F2775488%2F131020_rally_600.jpg&h=a7cf6a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統大選11月3日舉行，確診新冠肺炎的美國總統特朗普表示，連續數天的新冠病毒檢測都呈陰性反應。特朗普恢復競選活動，周一（12日）於佛羅里達州的集會上並無佩戴口罩，更表示希望親吻在場的所有支持者。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普（Donald Trump）周一晚於奧蘭多桑福德國際機場舉行戶外集會，在場約有數千人聚集，不少人都沒有戴口罩。特朗普也沒有戴口罩出席集會，並表示他已經歷新冠肺炎疫情並對此免疫，形容自己感覺充滿力量（feel so powerful）。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普將口罩投擲向聚集的人群，更揚言要親吻在場支持者：<br />\n<br />\n（I&rsquo;ll kiss everyone in that audience. I&rsquo;ll kiss the guys and the beautiful women. I&rsquo;ll just give you a big fat kiss.）<br />\n<br />\n美國的新冠肺炎疫情肆虐之際，特朗普於集會上仍呼籲支持者外出。特朗普解釋指，他覺得擊敗某些東西的感覺很良好。他承認外出會有風險（risky），但認為民眾仍有必要外出（but you have to get out）。"},{"pid":"b0b496b19fdf3b1cd64ab721792f5f3de886b0f3","tid":2241070,"uid":4780,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"中完武肺short 撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5da4938b595ba23870f3cf9f909e377d7aaddc5","tid":2241070,"uid":244358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13c0a1b62d26d3a749c6fd5cfb95b563499666a","tid":2241070,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0